{"vars": {}, "config": {"p1": "James Bond's (Pierce Brosnan) stunt pistol and holster from Lee Tamahori's Bond film Die Another Day (2002). The pistol was used by Brosnan during the film's climactic action sequence aboard the Antonov aircraft.", "p2": "Die Another Day was the twentieth entry in the Eon Productions James Bond series and marked the franchise's fortieth anniversary. The film grossed over $431 million worldwide upon its theatrical release in 2002.", "concerns": "[{\"paragraph\":\"P1\",\"field\":\"scene_context\",\"concern\":\"scene_context is present but brief; P1 scene anchor may lack specificity\"},{\"paragraph\":\"P3\",\"item_id\":\"91045\",\"field\":\"dimensions_metric\",\"concern\":\"dimensions_metric populated but dimensions_imperial absent; imperial line will be omitted\"}]", "p3_drafts": "[{\"item_id\":\"91044\",\"item_title\":\"Stunt Pistol\",\"text\":\"This cast zinc alloy stunt pistol measures 28 x 12 x 4 cm (11\\\" x 4.75\\\" x 1.5\\\") and weighs 0.32 kg. The grip panels are rubber and the barrel shows light scuffing consistent with production use. Condition is rated Fine.\"},{\"item_id\":\"91045\",\"item_title\":\"Holster\",\"text\":\"The brown leather holster measures 18 x 9 x 3 cm (7\\\" x 3.5\\\" x 1.25\\\") and is constructed with stitched reinforcement at the retention strap. Condition is rated Very Good with minor surface wear to the exterior.\"}]", "p3_merged": "This lot comprises a cast zinc alloy stunt pistol and its accompanying leather holster, both production-used in Die Another Day. The pistol (28 x 12 x 4 cm; 0.32 kg) retains rubber grip panels and displays light scuffing to the barrel consistent with on-set handling, graded Fine. The holster (18 x 9 x 3 cm) is constructed in brown leather with stitched reinforcement at the retention strap and is graded Very Good with minor surface wear.", "p4_drafts": "[{\"item_id\":\"91044\",\"item_title\":\"Stunt Pistol\",\"text\":\"The pistol comes from the personal collection of stunt coordinator Gary Powell, who served as stunt coordinator on Die Another Day. It is accompanied by a letter of authenticity from Eon Productions. The piece has been photo-matched to frame 01:14:22 of the theatrical cut.\"},{\"item_id\":\"91045\",\"item_title\":\"Holster\",\"text\":\"OMIT_PARAGRAPH\"}]", "p4_merged": "The pistol originates from the personal collection of stunt coordinator Gary Powell and is accompanied by a letter of authenticity from Eon Productions. It has been photo-matched to frame 01:14:22 of the theatrical cut.", "lot_context": "{\"lot_id\":\"84201\",\"category\":\"Props\",\"estimate_min\":\"15000\",\"estimate_max\":\"20000\",\"estimate_currency\":\"USD\"}", "run_start_ms": "1720441823004"}}
